-- Merafe-Xstrata Venture Says First-Half Ferrochrome Production Climbed 149%
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-27T06:04:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/merafe-xstrata-venture-says-first-half-ferrochrome-production-climbed-149-.html

          
          
             Merafe Resources Ltd. said
ferrochrome production from its venture with Xstrata Plc during
the six months through June rose 149 percent from a year
earlier.  
          
          


  


        